    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Doors of several hinged horizontal sections, that slide up along tracks to end in a horizontal position over the space to be entered; common in the United States as garage doors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
